reviewText: Mighty Fine for a DeTomaso Enthusiast.

Poorly made video on a great car. Editing is very poor. Save your money and buy one of the great books on panteras. This video is a waste of time for most people who have a general interest in panteras.

My husband owns a Pantera, so I bought this video for a Christmas present.  If you like Pantera vehicles it's sort of fun - until it starts interviewing Pantera owners. Pantera fans want to see cars!  My husband watched it once and packed it away.
